    Append datasets

    append.Rd

    Usage

    append(...)

    Arguments

    ...

    Data frames to combine.

    Value

    A data frame

    Details

    append stacks multiple datasets.

    See also

    Other Data Management: codebook(), count_functions, cut(), tag_duplicates()
